43-1945|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=2LBvZPXmmqoC&pg=PA218|year=2001|publisher=Lexington Books|isbn=978-0-7391-0195-7}}\n* [[Walid Phares]], ''Lebanese Christian Nationalism: The Rise and Fall of an Ethnic Resistance'' (Boulder, Colo.: L. Rienner, 1995). {{ISBN|1-55587-535-1}}\n* {{Cite book|ref=harv|last=Phayer|first=Michael|authorlink=Michael Phayer|title=The Catholic Church and the Holocaust, 1930\u20131965|year=2000|location=Bloomington and Indianapolis|publisher=Indiana University Press|url=https://archive.org/details/catholicchurchho00phay|url-access=registration}}\n* {{Cite book|ref=harv|last=Phayer|first=Michael|authorlink=Michael Phayer|title=Pius XII, the Holocaust, and the Cold War|year=2008|location=Bloomington and Indianapolis|publisher=Indiana University Press|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=CgTZAAAAMAAJ}}\n* {{Cite book|ref=harv|last=Pollard|first=John F.|authorlink=John F. Pollard|chapter=Clerical Fascism: Context, Overview and Conclusion|title=Clerical Fascism in Interwar Europe|year=2008|location=London-New York|publisher=Routledge|pages=221-234|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=KcfhAQAAQBAJ}}\n* {{Cite book|ref=harv|last=Rhodes|first=Anthony|authorlink=Anthony Rhodes|title=The Vatican in the Age of the Dictators 1922-1945|year=1973|location=New York|publisher=Holt, Rinehart and Winston|url=https://archive.org/details/vaticaninageof00rhod|url-access=registration|isbn=9780030077364}}\n* {{Cite book|ref=harv|last=Rivelli|first=Marco Aurelio|authorlink=Marco Aurelio Rivelli|year=1998|title=Le g\u00e9nocide occult\u00e9: \u00c9tat Ind\u00e9pendant de Croatie 1941\u20131945|language=French|trans-title=Hidden Genocide: The Independent State of Croatia 1941\u20131945|location=Lausanne|publisher=L'age d'Homme|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=QwBnceJfwgUC|isbn=9782825111529}}\n* {{Cite book|ref=harv|last=Rivelli|first=Marco Aurelio|authorlink=Marco Aurelio Rivelli|title=L'arcivescovo del genocidio: Monsignor Stepinac, il Vaticano e l