ey Graham]], U.S. Senator (R-SC)<ref>{{cite web|title=Sen. @ThomTillis stood with me against the liberal mob to confirm Justice Kavanaugh, and he will continue to stand for @realDonaldTrump's agenda of a strong military, lower taxes, and conservative judges. This is why I strongly urge my neighbors in NC to re-elect @ThomTillis.|url=https://twitter.com/LindseyGrahamSC/status/1136981131662962689|website=Twitter|author=Lindsey Graham}}</ref>\n*[[Marsha Blackburn]], U.S. Senator (R-TN)<ref>https://twitter.com/VoteMarsha/status/1234482083109777410</ref>\n*[[John R. Bolton|John Bolton]], former [[United States National Security Advisor]]<ref>https://nypost.com/2019/09/13/john-bolton-returns-to-former-position-as-head-of-two-pacs/</ref> \n*[[Nikki Haley]], former [[United States Ambassador to the United Nations]] and former [[Governor of South Carolina]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/ThomTillis/status/1230635125282615296|title=So thankful to have Ambassador @NikkiHaley\u2019s support. She has been a strong leader on sound, conservative priorities and I am honored to have her on our team.|work=Twitter|author=Thom Tillis}}</ref>\n*[[Ted Budd]], U.S. Representative (R-NC)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/buddforcongress/status/1232080763748855808|title=My wife Amy Kate and I just voted in the North Carolina primary. I am proud to vote for @realDonaldTrump, @ThomTillis, and @DanForestNC|work=Twitter|author=Ted Budd}}</ref>\n\n;Organizations\n* [[Susan B. Anthony List]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Thom Tillis |url=https://www.sba-list.org/candidate/thom-tillis |website=Susan B. Anthony List |accessdate=February 27, 2020}}</ref>\n}}\n\n{{Endorsements box\n| title = Cal Cunningham (D)\n| list = \n;Federal officials\n*[[Alma Adams]], U.S. Representative from [[North Carolina's 12th congressional district]]<ref name=\"CalDelegationEndorsement\">{{cite news|last=Cunningham|first=Cal|title=North Carolina Democratic Congressional Delegation Endorses Cal Cunningham|url=https: